shit is a st fork that:
- Loads settings from Xresources. See https://git.io/vVisW
- Live-reloads settings from xrdb on USR1 signal (like termite)
- Has some patches applied. See https://git.io/vVoKK
- Is available as an AUR package `shit-git` (binary and man still named st)

st can be found at: http://st.suckless.org/
